00:29:13.760 --> 00:29:16.640
 Because this can apply to different models.

00:29:16.640 --> 00:29:19.320
 It's just this one happens to be applying to the article model.

00:29:19.320 --> 00:29:23.840
 So I've built a super generic owner capability

00:29:23.840 --> 00:29:26.280
 that I can use over and over.

00:29:26.280 --> 00:29:30.080
 And just take your time, watch this more than once,

00:29:30.080 --> 00:29:34.440
 review object orientation, figure this out.

00:29:34.440 --> 00:29:38.640
 It's hard-- it's hard for me, when I'm teaching,

