 Object orientation is cool because it

00:29:44.400 --> 00:29:47.480
 can let you write these super elegant and very reliable.

00:29:47.480 --> 00:29:50.480
 The fewer lines of code you write, the more reliable it is.

00:29:50.480 --> 00:29:52.520
 But the harder it is to understand.

